WEBVTT

1
00:05:36.810 --> 00:05:39.140 
都是他出的好主意才有了这次大惨败
This entire fiasco was his big idea.

2
00:05:39.140 --> 00:05:41.850 
他开口最好就是说辞职
He-he opens his mouth, it better be to resign.

3
00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:44.410 
你可能不爱听
You may not like it,

4
00:05:44.410 --> 00:05:46.410 
但凡事有原则
but there are principles involved.

5
00:05:46.850 --> 00:05:48.870 
-什么原则  -相称性
- What principles? - Proportionality.

6
00:05:48.870 --> 00:05:51.170 
他们杀了我们的总统  杀了我们的特种部队
They killed our president. They killed our operatives.

7
00:05:51.170 --> 00:05:52.750 
和必要性
And necessity.

8
00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:54.010 
真正的问题是
Here's the real question:

9
00:05:54.010 --> 00:05:57.440 
到底要发生什么样的惨剧
what calamity has to occur before you finally admit

10
00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:58.890 
你才能承认应该行动起来了
it's time to do something?

11
00:05:58.890 --> 00:06:01.300 
是该行动  但不是这么行动
Something, yes, not this,

12
00:06:01.300 --> 00:06:03.520 
不是全面入侵一个已经声明
not a full-scale invasion of a nuclear power

13
00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:06.290 
绝不允许我们越过边界的有核国家
that has said they will not tolerate our crossing their border.

14
00:06:06.290 --> 00:06:09.600 
你他妈觉得最后会是什么结果
How in the fucking world do you think that'll end?

